                   "biography":  {
                                     "value":  "\u003cp\u003eGrÃ©nvÃ¶rÃ°r (meaning \"green guardian\") is the keeper of the Green Heart\u0027s threshold â€” an ancient elf-adjacent being whose skin has the color of deep bark and whose eyes are gold like the light in the central tree. She has tended the grove since before human kingdoms had names. She is not hostile but is not warm either â€” observant, waiting, assessing. She speaks with a voice like wind through leaves.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eShe is accompanied by SÃ­l and ÃžrÃºÃ°r, holders of the root-song â€” two silent elves who step forward only when the Old Compact is invoked. Together they represent the Green Heart\u0027s consent.\u003c/p\u003e",
                                     "director":  "\u003csection class=\"secret\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBEAT 22 â€” THE GREEN HEART AUDIENCE\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eShe/her. Ancient elf-adjacent. Keeper of the grove\u0027s threshold. She is not an obstacle to overcome â€” she is the Green Heart\u0027s consent. She and her companions must hear from the party why Kaelen\u0027s sacrifice is worthy of the grove\u0027s participation.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eROLE:\u003c/strong\u003e Negotiation target. She assesses whether Kaelen\u0027s transformation receives the grove\u0027s full blessing (making the binding permanent), partial acceptance (binding holds but requires tending), or withdrawal (binding is weak â€” cracks remain).\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDEMEANOR:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cem\u003eInterest rises:\u003c/em\u003e Her ancient face becomes almost peaceful. Gold eyes brighten. \"You speak truth. The roots confirm it.\"\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cem\u003eInterest flat:\u003c/em\u003e Unmoved. \"You have not convinced me. Try again, or accept the grove\u0027s minimal blessing.\"\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cem\u003eInterest drops:\u003c/em\u003e Expression hardens. Light in the tree dims. \"That argument is beneath this moment.\"\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cem\u003ePatience at 1:\u003c/em\u003e \"We are running out of time. Speak if you have something else to say.\"\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKEY LINES:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\"You bring the Seventh. We have been watching. We have been waiting to see who would come, and what she would do when she arrived.\"\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\"Welcome to the Green Heart. I am GrÃ©nvÃ¶rÃ°r, keeper of the grove\u0027s threshold. We have tended this place since before your kingdoms had names. We will know, before you speak, whether you come to save or to steal.\"\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003c/section\u003e",
